attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Gary Greene -

data.description: Impressive 4-bedroom, 3-full bath, and one-half bath residence offers an abundance of space and an array of desirable features. As you enter, a dedicated office/study welcomes you, providing the perfect space for productive work or serene contemplation. Abundant natural light fills the open living spaces, perfect for daily life and gatherings. The chef's kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample storage, and a sprawling island, making meal preparation a pleasure. An expansive gameroom offers versatile entertainment options. Retreat to the spacious primary suite with a spa-like bathroom, while three additional well-appointed bedrooms ensure comfort for all. A 3-car garage with tandem parking provides ample storage. Outside, a covered patio invites al fresco dining and relaxation. A whole-house generator ensures uninterrupted comfort during outages. In Artavia, residents enjoy DAPPLE PARK, a five-acre lake, parks, splash pads, trails, meditation centers, FitCenter, Palate Cafe, and more.
